Company Overview of Brave Asset Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Brave Asset Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals and charitable organizations. The firm manages separate client-focused balanced portfolios. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets. The firm also invests in options. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. Brave Asset Management, Inc. was founded in 1992 and is based in Summit, New Jersey.


