                      BRAVE ASSET MANAGEMENT INC
                    

•   SUMMIT, NJ
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Brave Asset Management is based out of Summit. Brave Asset Management is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $227,948,557 (Form ADV from 2017-03-14).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $171,023,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 34.6%. Brave Asset Management's largest holding is iShares S&P US Preferrd Stock Index Fund with shares held of 244,430.  Brave Asset Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 14 13Fs and  12 13D/G filings in our database for Brave Asset Management. 
                                           






